name: The Journey of Sinta - CBGB & OMFUG
description:
Still in New York, this time Sinta visited CBGB.
CBGB is one of the historical places for the music industry. CBGB was founded by Hilly Kristal. 
In its day, CBGB became the place where punk rock music developed in New York.
In 2005, CBGB was declared closed and has now changed to a John Varvatos store.
